The paper deals with a technique for estimating similarity between sets, which is a common problem in information retrieval (IR) and databases (DB). The technique involves hashing, which is a common tool in data structures (DS). The paper also proposes an improved algorithm, which falls under the category of machine learning (LG) and statistics (SI). Therefore, the most likely sub-categories are cs.DS, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.DB, and cs.SI.
